Clear Babur's mine
It is said that the harpies in the southeast of the remote mountains have a great treasure. Collect the treasure and bring it to the village!
#subobj  1
Find the western chest
Locate the chest at the east of the mine. Its content might be well guarded.
#subobj  2
Find the northern chest
The second chest should be at the far end. In the north-east, dead end of the mine.
#subobj  3
Kill the first group of armadillos.
There should be five armadillos guarding the north-west part of the mine.
#subobj  4
Kill the second group of armadillos.
There are five more armadillos guarding the north part of the mine
